nodes.text: Kamil Lemieszewski (born June 17, 1983) is a Polish actor who portrayed a Jakku Villager in Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens, an X-Wing Pilot in Rogue One: A Star Wars Story, and the Skipper aboard Dryden Vos' starship from Solo: A Star Wars Story.
